    <h1 class="headline super bold">
        Michael Rosenblatt
    </h1>

    <h1 class="headline medium hairline">
    Michael is the Founder and Managing Director for <a href='http://www.seamlesspd.com' target='_blank'><i>Seamless Product Development</i></a> Company, with presence in Boulder, Silicon Valley and Boston. Seamless is a concept-to-production consulting firm that specializes in evaluating and developing new technologies for large-scale production applications.
    </h1>
    <p>
    For nearly 20 years, Michael has been assembling high caliber teams to solve hard technical problems. Michael technical background is in product design and robotics, spending much of my early career developing groundbreaking Mobile, Internet-of-Things and Wearable products at tech giants <i>Apple</i> and <i>Samsung Electronics</i>.
    <br><br>
    Michael is assembling fast-response, flexible teams of electrical, mechanical, and embedded systems engineers in the Boulder-Denver area to service clients around the globe, with the goal of helping companies develop innovative, differentiated solutions to meaningful problems. This includes end-to-end product development, auxiliary engineering support for an internal team, or planning long-term technology strategy.
    </p>

